{"tid":1103424,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拜仁訓練爆發內訌！兩大將竟動手互毆","createTime":"2019-04-12T11:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T03:13:57.000Z","uid":147522,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"42b695638efd68f5f73f0df2874abf54c9dd74a8","tid":1103424,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:40:44.000Z","msg":"　　拜仁在訓練中爆發了內訌。根據德國媒體的報導，利雲（R.Lewandowski）與高文（R.Koeman）在訓練中大打出手，最終還是隊友將兩人分了開來。<br />\n<br />\n　　據《圖片報》等媒體的消息，在週四拜仁的隊內訓練中，利雲與高文這兩人發生了衝突。兩人的矛盾從口頭迅速升級為了肢體上的碰撞。<br />\n<br />\n　　據悉，在訓練場上，是利雲方面先對高文進行挑釁，高文也不饒人，同樣以惡語相向，你來我往之間，衝突迅速升級，兩人開始動手互毆。<br />\n<br />\n　　最終，兩名後衛蘇尼（N.Sule）和保定（J.Boateng）將利雲和高文分開，製止了衝突，隊內其他球員也過來幫忙勸解。而在這次衝突過後，主教練高華（N.Kovac）沒有中止訓練，而是讓球隊繼續進行訓練計劃，利雲和高文兩人也都留在了訓練場上。"},{"pid":"3a8e02408306f010fccfe4bb47fbc7adfe6cd292","tid":1103424,"uid":51529,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:43:46.000Z","msg":"以為潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a01a2b78dde442a1dce169d0cea606047a2a5e","tid":1103424,"uid":42246,"like":31,"dislike":8,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:44:29.000Z","msg":"算啦 垃圾聯賽垃圾球會垃圾球員垃圾球迷<br />\n公海基本上冇人想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746c7183c76d88c97e6e4a95e4abc73d0161570e","tid":1103424,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:44:56.000Z","msg":"往死裡打"},{"pid":"53df2053aa182690faf27333d0ff1950ded7bf9c","tid":1103424,"uid":123304,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:45:22.000Z","msg":"往死裡打"},{"pid":"d2eff5fd51cd000ab10ddff3e35431cd0c1cc7f6","tid":1103424,"uid":2914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:45:22.000Z","msg":"瘋了，瘋了"},{"pid":"6ab806cc12e2cb9e8055a20acf2856d8e9c80e3c","tid":1103424,"uid":8566,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"R.Koeman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n朗奴高文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0bb566c9fef4da1097daa38745c4cea2527818","tid":1103424,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:47:13.000Z","msg":"利雲應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6c577d4abbc88905ad49d61df5f7d2e9dfa3c2","tid":1103424,"uid":20924,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"利雲（R.Lewandowski）與高文（<span style=\"color: red;\">R.Koeman</span>）在訓練中大打出手，最終還是隊友將兩人分了開來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n變左朗奴高文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a41966db4ab47b16c2ab10bd8cd67e908c0ae5","tid":1103424,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:50:59.000Z","msg":"往死裏打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5cc7b5740b571eb1c3bf903dcbd34b950221c7","tid":1103424,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f6c577d4abbc88905ad49d61df5f7d2e9dfa3c2","tid":1103424,"uid":20924,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"利雲（R.Lewandowski）與高文（<span style=\"color: red;\">R.Koeman</span>）在訓練中大打出手，最終還是隊友將兩人分了開來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n變左朗奴高文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:53:08.000Z","msg":"@牙蓋"},{"pid":"4b216a9591bb0c7e7569abaf14ab51e301694f15","tid":1103424,"uid":26862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:55:28.000Z","msg":"高文打女人就叻<br />\n對住利雲撚有得打咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e148ab5c6378091cd0374404a117d0588fa857","tid":1103424,"uid":242358,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:58:45.000Z","msg":"曼聯隊長卡域克在接受曼聯足球報訪問中，炮轟盧卡古和普巴等人，稱他們就是曼聯更衣室的毒瘤。 <br />\n<br />\n卡域克談到：「如果你作為球隊隊長，你本應該感到高興因為這是一種榮譽，你可以帶領你的球隊不斷前進，你就是球隊領袖，但是我從來沒有享受過這樣的待遇，球隊有太多超級球星，他們踢球都是以我為主，更衣室經常發生矛盾，開始我還試著去阻止，後來他們直接叫我閉嘴，我根本感覺不到自己就是隊長。」<br />\n<br />\n卡域克：「在球隊普巴常常痛駡一些年輕球員，這再正常不過了，不過也有球員被激怒的時候，記得在一場熱身賽中場休息的時候，普巴上半場踢得很不自在，回到更衣室用水瓶怒砸一位才進一隊的球員，當時很多隊友都已經無法容忍普巴的所作所為，再加上那些常被他欺辱的球員，無法阻止的一幕發生了，至少有10人群毆了普巴，你可以想像被10人群毆的滋味，在一旁的馬迪爾更是拍手叫好，不停大喊：『給我打，把他往死裡打！』當時伊巴、馬達這兩位大佬並沒有參與這次毆鬥，他們也沒有阻止，好像一切與他倆無關。」<br />\n<br />\n卡域克：「當發生那件事情後，普巴的更衣櫃多了一根鐵棍，我想他是用來防身吧，在剛過去的曼市打比盧卡古正是用這根鐵棍報復了馬迪爾，在打比戰結束後，全隊回到更衣室，馬迪爾諷刺性地說道：『9000萬前鋒，漂亮的助攻。』」<br />\n<br />\n「盧卡古臉色僵硬但並沒有回應什麼，只是默默地走出更衣室，這不像盧卡古的性格，果然在盧卡古再次回到更衣室的時候手裡握著一根木棍，在馬迪爾毫無防備的情況一棍打下，馬迪爾挨那一下著實不輕，趴在地上痛苦地抬頭才看到是打他那人正是盧卡古，不等馬迪爾起身，盧卡古又是一頓亂棍爆打，馬迪爾在地上滿地打滾不停求饒，在一旁的普巴可不會放過這樣的機會不斷說道：『羅美路，打狗，用力打，往死裡給我打，打狗怎能少了我。』」<br />\n<br />\n「普巴的防身鐵棍終於派上了用場，可惜一棍下去馬迪爾就昏死了過去，打得興起的盧卡古怒了，朝著普巴吼道：『這下還還怎麼打，你該滾一邊去！』普巴也不甘示弱：『你再說一遍，有種你重複一遍！』盧卡古沒有再回應普巴什麼，如果普巴手上沒有鐵棍那麼他們肯定會打起來。當時我身邊的隊醫嘴裡不停地說：『瘋了，瘋了，都已經瘋了。』」"},{"pid":"92083e24ce496717729798c4239fd4c44862a3af","tid":1103424,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a8e02408306f010fccfe4bb47fbc7adfe6cd292","tid":1103424,"uid":51529,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:43:46.000Z","msg":"以為潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b4351d6daa17c6782731ab3484465faf6d71f5","tid":1103424,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f6c577d4abbc88905ad49d61df5f7d2e9dfa3c2","tid":1103424,"uid":20924,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"利雲（R.Lewandowski）與高文（<span style=\"color: red;\">R.Koeman</span>）在訓練中大打出手，最終還是隊友將兩人分了開來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n變左朗奴高文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:27:30.000Z","msg":"Ronald Koeman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ecf6cee789f80c4f3a78d7087cccd0a54ae3da6","tid":1103424,"uid":35217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b216a9591bb0c7e7569abaf14ab51e301694f15","tid":1103424,"uid":26862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:55:28.000Z","msg":"高文打女人就叻<br />\n對住利雲撚有得打咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:27:37.000Z","msg":"利雲老婆好似空手道定唔知咩道<br />\n平時切磋開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ec195cc3cb785ff6d3d1ae4de01af71807e19c","tid":1103424,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df5cc7b5740b571eb1c3bf903dcbd34b950221c7","tid":1103424,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f6c577d4abbc88905ad49d61df5f7d2e9dfa3c2","tid":1103424,"uid":20924,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:47:37.000Z","msg":"利雲（R.Lewandowski）與高文（<span style=\"color: red;\">R.Koeman</span>）在訓練中大打出手，最終還是隊友將兩人分了開來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n變左朗奴高文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:53:08.000Z","msg":"@牙蓋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:40:50.000Z","msg":"利雲咁忍得"},{"pid":"6018bbc8ce0a50d79580c2432105d530a12ee308","tid":1103424,"uid":60695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:49:22.000Z","msg":"r.koeman?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a2bce80e79a1b49555aa91bf3b7860c0790210","tid":1103424,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ab806cc12e2cb9e8055a20acf2856d8e9c80e3c","tid":1103424,"uid":8566,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T11:45:58.000Z","msg":"R.Koeman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n朗奴高文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:54:27.000Z","msg":"利雲唔啱啦<br />\n<br />\n虐老都算<br />\n呢次算係恰低能仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://dutchsoccersite.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/Koeman-R-thon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdutchsoccersite.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F05%2FKoeman-R-thon.jpg&h=9d0f5ead&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9eaf40a7a8ea3485c49db5f1acbf723df597e090","tid":1103424,"uid":63877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:58:50.000Z","msg":"呢隊西波好似成日都傳出訓練場打架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前唔記得甘美治定梅拿 都唔係第一次"},{"pid":"2ed1a356fa4351f06beb9d46d1a88245fbe48151","tid":1103424,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9eaf40a7a8ea3485c49db5f1acbf723df597e090","tid":1103424,"uid":63877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2